In future videos we'll try to think about,

00:03:55.750 --> 00:03:57.551
how do you relate these points,

00:03:57.551 --> 00:04:00.378
the focus and directrix, to the actual,

00:04:00.378 --> 00:04:03.317
to the actual equation,
or the actual equation

00:04:03.317 --> 00:04:04.967
for a parabola.

